{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778770029340,"sessionID":"ses_1d9115b96ffe8x5ZpDXmUHBSCU","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"write:0","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"id: hyp-20260514-001-r7s0\ntitle: \"Forward exact load_data from MEM to EX to eliminate load-use stalls\"\ncategory: micro_opt\nmotivation: |\n  Load-use stalls are the primary IPC bottleneck in the 5-stage baseline.\n  A LOAD followed by a dependent ALU instruction currently stalls for one\n  cycle.  Previous MEM-to-EX forwarding attempts failed because they\n  forwarded raw dmem_rdata (wrong for byte/halfword loads) or added\n  unused ports to forward_unit (compile failure).  By replicating the\n  full mem_stage byte-alignment and sign-extension logic in the\n  top-level forwarding path, the forwarded value matches the WB write\n  value exactly, satisfying RVFI.  Re-using the existing forward_unit\n  encoding (EX_MEM=2'd1) avoids port changes.\nhypothesis: |\n  In core.sv, replicate mem_stage's load_data computation\n  combinationally and drive it onto fwd_ex_mem whenever EX/MEM holds a\n  load (mem_read=1).  This lets the existing forward_unit and ex_stage\n  muxes route the loaded value to a dependent instruction in EX,\n  eliminating the one-cycle load-use stall for all load widths.  In\n  hazard_unit.sv, clear load_use_hazard so the pipeline no longer\n  stalls on any load-use.  During a dmem stall the pipeline still\n  freezes via dmem_stall, so the forwarding path is only active when\n  dmem_rdata is valid.\nexpected_impact:\n  fitness_delta_pct: 4\n  confidence: medium\nchanges:\n  - file: rtl/core.sv\n    description: \"Replicate mem_stage load_data extraction and sign-extension; mux it onto fwd_ex_mem when EX/MEM.ctrl.mem_read is set, otherwise pass ex_mem_w.alu_result as before.\"\n  - file: rtl/hazard_unit.sv\n    description: \"Set load_use_hazard = 1'b0 unconditionally; MEM-to-EX forwarding now covers the case that the old stall protected.\"\n","filePath":"/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep3/cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260514-001-r7s0.yaml"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep3/cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260514-001-r7s0.yaml","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260514-001-r7s0.yaml","time":{"start":1778770029329,"end":1778770029339}},"id":"prt_e26f485ee001kDwDGGhDYYYm6h","sessionID":"ses_1d9115b96ffe8x5ZpDXmUHBSCU","messageID":"msg_e26eea4a2001Sau7motlOnRDwB"}}
