{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778756320054,"sessionID":"ses_1d9e1a84affe3RilYSpocuFUh4","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"write:1","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"id: hyp-20260514-002-r2s1\ntitle: Early branch and jump resolution in ID stage\ncategory: structural\nmotivation: |\n  The current 5-stage pipeline resolves all control-flow instructions in EX,\n  causing a 2-cycle bubble for every taken branch and jump. CoreMark's\n  tight loops and frequent function calls spend a significant fraction of\n  cycles recovering from these mispredicts. Moving branch condition\n  evaluation and jump target computation to the ID stage cuts the penalty\n  to 1 cycle, directly improving iterations/cycle.\nhypothesis: |\n  Relocate unconditional jump (JAL/JALR) target calculation and conditional\n  branch resolution from EX to ID. Add operand forwarding paths from\n  EX/MEM and MEM/WB into the ID stage so branches dependent on recent\n  results resolve without stalling. Introduce a load-to-branch stall in\n  the hazard unit when a branch in ID consumes a load result still in EX.\n  Pipeline an early-redirect flag so EX does not re-assert flush on an\n  instruction already redirected in ID.\nexpected_impact:\n  fitness_delta_pct: 8\n  confidence: medium\nchanges:\n  - file: rtl/core_pkg.sv\n    description: Add early_redirect bit to id_ex_t pipeline bundle.\n  - file: rtl/id_stage.sv\n    description: |\n      Insert branch target adder, branch condition comparator, and\n      forwarding muxes for rs1/rs2. Drive id_redirect and\n      id_redirect_target to IF stage.\n  - file: rtl/if_stage.sv\n    description: Accept id_redirect/id_redirect_target and prioritize them over EX redirect.\n  - file: rtl/hazard_unit.sv\n    description: |\n      Assert flush_if (but not flush_id) on id_redirect. Add\n      load-to-branch stall detection when a branch source matches a\n      load in EX.\n  - file: rtl/ex_stage.sv\n    description: Suppress redirect output when the id_ex_t early_redirect flag is set.\n  - file: rtl/core.sv\n    description: Wire id_redirect signals between stages and update forwarding connections.\n","filePath":"/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep3/cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260514-002-r2s1.yaml"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep3/cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260514-002-r2s1.yaml","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260514-002-r2s1.yaml","time":{"start":1778756320050,"end":1778756320053}},"id":"prt_e262359bc001kryMw82R5Lt6zW","sessionID":"ses_1d9e1a84affe3RilYSpocuFUh4","messageID":"msg_e26233ce4001iK8L9mrb1WEo5w"}}
