{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778766745380,"sessionID":"ses_1d93f6632ffefVNacNrTr0HXtD","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"write:0","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"id: hyp-20260514-002-r6s1\ntitle: Forward exact load_data from MEM to EX to eliminate load-use stalls\ncategory: structural\nmotivation: |\n  The 5-stage pipeline currently stalls for one cycle on every load-use hazard.\n  CoreMark contains frequent pointer-chasing and array indexing patterns that\n  trigger these stalls. Previous attempts failed because the forwarded value\n  did not exactly match the WB write value. mem_stage already computes the\n  fully byte-aligned and sign-extended load_data combinationally; exposing it\n  to the EX-stage forward mux allows us to remove the stall entirely without\n  duplicating extraction logic.\nhypothesis: |\n  Add a combinational load_data output to mem_stage and use it in core.sv to\n  drive the fwd_ex_mem input to ex_stage whenever the instruction in EX/MEM\n  is a LOAD (ctrl.mem_read). Remove the load_use_hazard detection from\n  hazard_unit so that a dependent instruction can enter EX in the same cycle\n  the LOAD is in MEM. This reuses the existing forward_unit encoding\n  (fwd_rs1_sel/fwd_rs2_sel = 2'b01) and requires no changes to ex_stage or\n  forward_unit.\nexpected_impact:\n  fitness_delta_pct: 7\n  confidence: medium\nchanges:\n  - file: rtl/mem_stage.sv\n    description: \"Expose the internal combinational load_data signal as an additional output port.\"\n  - file: rtl/core.sv\n    description: \"Mux fwd_ex_mem between ex_mem_w.alu_result and mem_stage.load_data based on ex_mem_w.ctrl.mem_read.\"\n  - file: rtl/hazard_unit.sv\n    description: \"Remove load_use_hazard from stall_if, stall_id, and flush_id logic.\"\n","filePath":"/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep3/cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260514-002-r6s1.yaml"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep3/cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260514-002-r6s1.yaml","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260514-002-r6s1.yaml","time":{"start":1778766745366,"end":1778766745378}},"id":"prt_e26c27a1e001rM6tzrWbxj3hfE","sessionID":"ses_1d93f6632ffefVNacNrTr0HXtD","messageID":"msg_e26c09a0a001AsLujVp3t5so0a"}}
