{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778753678035,"sessionID":"ses_1da0815ffffeBXuejAGW6vwgt6","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"write:1","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"id: hyp-20260514-003-r1s2\ntitle: \"32-entry 2-bit dynamic branch predictor in IF stage\"\ncategory: predictor\nmotivation: |\n  The baseline always fetches pc+4 and only redirects after a branch resolves in EX,\n  costing a 2-cycle bubble for every taken branch. CoreMark is loop-heavy; even a\n  simple dynamic predictor eliminates most of these bubbles, directly improving IPC.\n  A 32-entry PHT adds only 64 flops and a small combinational read port, well within\n  the ~400 LUT4 headroom on the Tang Nano 20K.\nhypothesis: |\n  Add a 32-entry 2-bit saturating counter branch predictor (PHT) indexed by PC[6:2].\n  In the IF stage, detect conditional branches (opcode 1100011) and JAL (opcode 1101111);\n  extract the immediate via a small imm_gen instance and compute target = pc + imm.\n  Query the PHT for branches; always predict JAL as taken. A new predict_taken bit is\n  added to the IF/ID and ID/EX pipeline bundles. In EX, redirect is asserted only on\n  mispredict (predicted != actual outcome), with the redirect target selecting the\n  correct path (branch target or pc+4). The PHT is updated when a branch resolves in EX.\nexpected_impact:\n  fitness_delta_pct: 10\n  confidence: medium\nchanges:\n  - file: rtl/core_pkg.sv\n    description: \"Add predict_taken bit to if_id_t and id_ex_t pipeline structs.\"\n  - file: rtl/branch_predictor.sv\n    description: \"New 32-entry 2-bit saturating counter PHT module with async read and synchronous update.\"\n  - file: rtl/if_stage.sv\n    description: \"Add branch/JAL detection, imm_gen instance, target adder, and predictor integration to compute next_pc. Output predict_taken in IF/ID bundle.\"\n  - file: rtl/id_stage.sv\n    description: \"Pass predict_taken from IF/ID into the ID/EX register.\"\n  - file: rtl/ex_stage.sv\n    description: \"Change redirect logic to compare predicted vs actual outcome. Add predictor update output ports (update_en, update_pc, update_taken).\"\n  - file: rtl/core.sv\n    description: \"Instantiate branch_predictor, wire update signals from EX stage to predictor, and pass predict_taken through the pipeline.\"\n","filePath":"/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep3/cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260514-003-r1s2.yaml"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep3/cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260514-003-r1s2.yaml","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260514-003-r1s2.yaml","time":{"start":1778753678025,"end":1778753678034}},"id":"prt_e25fb07d9001Z7EVH3OjkgJ26o","sessionID":"ses_1da0815ffffeBXuejAGW6vwgt6","messageID":"msg_e25fae42a001Oeej2wn2pMwGKl"}}
