[causal_ch0] base: /Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep3/formal/riscv-formal/cores/bench-3434/../../cores/bench-3434/wrapper.sv:94: Warning: Range select [63:32] out of bounds on signal `\\rvfi_pc_wdata': Setting all 32 result bits to undef.\nSBY 14:43:44 [causal_ch0] base: /Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep3/formal/riscv-formal/cores/bench-3434/../../cores/bench-3434/wrapper.sv:95: Warning: Range select [63:32] out of bounds on signal `\\rvfi_mem_addr': Setting all 32 result bits to undef.\nSBY 14:43:44 [causal_ch0] base: /Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep3/formal/riscv-formal/cores/bench-3434/../../cores/bench-3434/wrapper.sv:96: Warning: Range select [7:4] out of bounds on signal `\\rvfi_mem_rmask': Setting all 4 result bits to undef.\nSBY 14:43:44 [causal_ch0] base: /Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep3/formal/riscv-formal/cores/bench-3434/../../cores/bench-3434/wrapper.sv:97: Warning: Range select [7:4] out of bounds on signal `\\rvfi_mem_wmask': Setting all 4 result bits to undef.\nSBY 14:43:44 [causal_ch0] base: /Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep3/formal/riscv-formal/cores/bench-3434/../../cores/bench-3434/wrapper.sv:98: Warning: Range select [63:32] out of bounds on signal `\\rvfi_mem_rdata': Setting all 32 result bits to undef.\nSBY 14:43:44 [causal_ch0] base: /Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep3/formal/riscv-formal/cores/bench-3434/../../cores/bench-3434/wrapper.sv:99: Warning: Range select [63:32] out of bounds on signal `\\rvfi_mem_wdata': Setting all 32 result bits to undef.\nSBY 14:43:44 [causal_ch0] base: /Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep3/formal/riscv-formal/cores/bench-3434/../../cores/bench-3434/wrapper.sv:39: ERROR: Cell instance refers to port io_rvfi_valid_1 which does not exist in module core!.\nSBY 14:43:45 [causal_ch0] base: finished (returncode=1)\nSBY 14:43:45 [causal_ch0] base: task failed. ERROR.\nSBY 14:43:45 [causal_ch0] summary: Elapsed clock time [H:MM:SS (secs)]: 0:00:00 (0)\nSBY 14:43:45 [causal_ch0] summary: Elapsed process time [H:MM:SS (secs)]: 0:00:00 (0)\nSBY 14:43:45 [causal_ch0] summary: engine_0 (smtbmc bitwuzla) did not return a status\nSBY 14:43:45 [causal_ch0] summary: engine_0 did not produce any traces\nSBY 14:43:45 [causal_ch0] DONE (ERROR, rc=16)\n\nFull run log: /Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep3/cores/bench/worktrees/hyp-20260514-002-r11s1/formal/last_run-3434.log\nPer-check logs in: /Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep3/cores/bench/worktrees/hyp-20260514-002-r11s1/formal/riscv-formal/cores/bench-3434/checks/<check>/logfile.txt\n","exit":1,"description":"Run formal verification for bench core","truncated":true,"outputPath":"/Users/bonetto/.local/share/opencode/tool-output/tool_e27965eb0001YeiOFNQGCrUbzu"},"title":"Run formal verification for bench core","time":{"start":1778780626794,"end":1778780626796}},"id":"prt_e27965381001kEh0yO9I3gLKW5","sessionID":"ses_1d86ae568ffeSeDaRHZ9bpqkcn","messageID":"msg_e279648b8001yPjQXhWdJV2CfD"}}
