{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778780633228,"sessionID":"ses_1d86ae568ffeSeDaRHZ9bpqkcn","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"functions.read:8","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep3/cores/bench/worktrees/hyp-20260514-002-r11s1/cores/bench/core.yaml"},"output":"<path>/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep3/cores/bench/worktrees/hyp-20260514-002-r11s1/cores/bench/core.yaml</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: name: bench\n2: description: Frozen LLM-benchmark fixture core. Identical RTL to baseline at the bench-fixture-v1\n3:   freeze point. The benchmark matrix clones from the bench-fixture-v1 orphan branch\n4:   and operates only on this directory.\n5: isa: rv32im\n6: nret: 1\n7: target_fpga: tang-nano-20k\n8: targets:\n9:   fmax_mhz: 135\n10:   lut4: 10000\n11:   coremark_iter_s: 300\n12:   coremark_per_mhz: 2.2\n13: current:\n14:   fmax_mhz: 165.51\n15:   lut4: 9927\n16:   ff: 1874\n17:   coremark_iter_s: 2.0e-06\n18:   coremark_per_mhz: 0.0\n19:   source_id: hyp-20260514-001-r8s0\n20:   updated: '2026-05-14T16:18:40.452720Z'\n\n(End of file - total 20 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"name: bench\ndescription: Frozen LLM-benchmark fixture core. Identical RTL to baseline at the bench-fixture-v1\n  freeze point. The benchmark matrix clones from the bench-fixture-v1 orphan branch\n  and operates only on this directory.\nisa: rv32im\nnret: 1\ntarget_fpga: tang-nano-20k\ntargets:\n  fmax_mhz: 135\n  lut4: 10000\n  coremark_iter_s: 300\n  coremark_per_mhz: 2.2\ncurrent:\n  fmax_mhz: 165.51\n  lut4: 9927\n  ff: 1874\n  coremark_iter_s: 2.0e-06\n  coremark_per_mhz: 0.0\n  source_id: hyp-20260514-001-r8s0\n  updated: '2026-05-14T16:18:40.452720Z'","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"cores/bench/core.yaml","time":{"start":1778780633220,"end":1778780633227}},"id":"prt_e279675e4001J4SROT66R4p0oR","sessionID":"ses_1d86ae568