{"type":"text","timestamp":1778780735122,"sessionID":"ses_1d86ae568ffeSeDaRHZ9bpqkcn","part":{"id":"prt_e2797f8c2001vsVQYWvUUK53rp","messageID":"msg_e2797efc9001LgNmBPGhar6Hpk","sessionID":"ses_1d86ae568ffeSeDaRHZ9bpqkcn","type":"text","text":"Implementation complete.\n\n**Changed file:** `cores/bench/rtl/alu.sv`\n\n**Summary of changes:**\n- Removed `mul_ss` (signed×signed) and `mul_su` (signed×unsigned) variables and their assignments.\n- Kept only `mul_uu = {32'b0, a} * {32'b0, b}` as the single 64-bit unsigned multiplier.\n- Added correction terms: `corr_a = a[31] ? b : 0` and `corr_b = b[31] ? a : 0`.\n- Updated the non-ALTOPS case statement:\n  - `ALU_MULH`:   `m_out = mul_uu[63:32] - corr_a - corr_b`\n  - `ALU_MULHSU`: `m_out = mul_uu[63:32] - corr_a`\n  - `ALU_MUL` and `ALU_MULHU` unchanged.\n- Left the ALTOPS branch, divider path, and fast-path 2:1 mux untouched.\n\n**Verification:**\n- Verilator lint: ✅ clean (no warnings/errors)\n- Formal `run_all.sh` (ALTOPS, nret=1): ✅ 53/53 passed on first attempt\n\n**Documentation:** `cores/bench/implementation_notes.md` written.","time":{"start":1778780731586,"end":1778780735121}}}
